snippet.title: Packed Train Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Packed Train is a casual puzzle game in which the player has to take cute little creatures of all sorts of shapes and pack them onto a train. Yeah, it's weird, but it's super fun! Enjoy the endless experience of beautiful and cute characters, colorful levels and cool gameplay. 

Available on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/821400/Packed_Train/
